Detailed Description

template<typename EvalT, typename Traits>
class LCM::KCPermeability< EvalT, Traits >

Evaluates permeability based on porosity through the Kozeny-Carman relation, either as a constant or a truncated KL expansion.The permeability is divided by viscosity.
